<br>
I think that everyone realizes that we &lt;as a guild&gt; don't feel that any one person should organize raids for everyone, i think that if we did that people would end up hitting the same places all the time, ToFS for example, not that i mind that if everyone is getting something out of it &lt;or at least alot of classes have a chance to get a drop <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  &gt; but i think that there should be a few raids for class specific stuff , such as a raid into somewhere where alot of things drop for pure casters or anouther place where things drop for mixed casters, that kind of thing.<br>
